<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBrunet-Rossinni_AK.2C_Austad_SN2004">Brunet-Rossinni AK, Austad SN (2004). "Aging studies on bats: a review". <i>BIOGERONTOLOGY</i> <b>5</b> (4): 211–222. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1023%2FB%3ABGEN.0000038022.65024.d8" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1023%2FB%3ABGEN.0000038022.65024.d8" rel="nofollow">10.1023/B:BGEN.0000038022.65024.d8</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15314271" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15314271">PMID 15314271</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Aging+studies+on+bats%3A+a+review&amp;rft.jtitle=BIOGERONTOLOGY&amp;rft.aulast=Brunet-Rossinni+AK%2C+Austad+SN&amp;rft.au=Brunet-Rossinni+AK%2C+Austad+SN&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=211%E2%80%93222&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1023%2FB%3ABGEN.0000038022.65024.d8&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/15314271&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Senescence"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> de Magalhaes JP, Costa J, Church GM. An analysis of the relationship between metabolism, developmental schedules, and longevity using phylogenetic independent contrasts. J Gerontol A Biol Sci Med Sci. 2007 Feb;62(2):149-60 <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17339640" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17339640">PMID 17339640</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSpeakman_JR.2C_Selman_C.2C_McLaren_JS.2C_Harper_EJ2002">Speakman JR, Selman C, McLaren JS, Harper EJ (2002). "<a href="http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/132/6/1583S" class="external text" title="http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/132/6/1583S" rel="nofollow">Living fast, dying when? The link between aging and energetics</a>". <i>THE JOURNAL OF NUTRITION</i> <b>132</b> (6, Supplement 2): 1583S–1597S. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12042467" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12042467">PMID 12042467</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/132/6/1583S" class="external free" title="http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/132/6/1583S" rel="nofollow">http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/132/6/1583S</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Living+fast%2C+dying+when%3F+The+link+between+aging+and+energetics&amp;rft.jtitle=THE+JOURNAL+OF+NUTRITION&amp;rft.aulast=Speakman+JR%2C+Selman+C%2C+McLaren+JS%2C+Harper+EJ&amp;rft.au=Speakman+JR%2C+Selman+C%2C+McLaren+JS%2C+Harper+EJ&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.volume=132&amp;rft.issue=6%2C+Supplement+2&amp;rft.pages=1583S%E2%80%931597S&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/12042467&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fjn.nutrition.org%2Fcgi%2Fcontent%2Ffull%2F132%2F6%2F1583S&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Senescence"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://pubs.niaaa.nih.gov/publications/arh23-4/272-283.pdf" class="external free" title="http://pubs.niaaa.nih.gov/publications/arh23-4/272-283.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://pubs.niaaa.nih.gov/publications/arh23-4/272-283.pdf</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
